ptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1019691, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! Through You I seek conquest, and through You I will achieve success, and through Muhammad, blessings of Allah be upon him and his progeny, I turn to (Allah). O Allah! Facilitate for me its complication and all complications, easy for me its difficulty and all difficulties, save me from its pain and all pains, and grant me its favours, its love, and take away from me its harm and its disgrace, surely You make to pass away and establishes what You pleases, and with You is the basis of the Book. Now surely the friends of Allah, they shall have no fear nor shall they grieve We are the apostles of your Lord; they shall by no means reach you; TAA HAA, HAA MEEM, they do not see. Surely We have placed chains on their necks, and these reach up to their chins, so they have their heads raised aloft. And We have made before them a barrier and a barrier behind them, then We have covered them over so that they do not see These are they on whose hearts and their hearing and their eyes Allah has set a seal, and these are the heedless ones Truly Allah knows what they hide and what they manifest; so Allah will suffice you against them, and He is the Hearing, the Knowing And you see them looking towards you, yet they do not see Deaf, dumb (and) blind, so they will not turn back TAA SEEN MEEM. These are the verses of the Book that makes (things) clear. Perhaps you will kill yourself with grief because they do not believe. If We please, We should send down upon them a sign from the heaven so that their necks should stoop to it.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Urdu": "انشاء اللہ ترجمہ جلد آرہا ہے", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA BEKA ASTAFTEHO WA BEKA ASTANJEHO WA BEMOHAMMADIN SALLAL LAAHO A’LAYHE WA AALEHI ATAWAJJAHO ALLAAHUMMA SAHHIL LEE HOZOONATAHU WA KULLA HOZOONATIN WA ZALLIL LEE SO-O’OBATAHU WA KULLA SO-O’OBATIN WAK FENEE MA-OOONATAHU WA KULLA MA-OONATIN WAR ZUQNEE MA’ROOFAHU WA WUDDAHU WAS RIF A’NNEE ZURRAHU WA MA-A’RRATAHU INNAKA TAMHOO MAA TASHAAA-O WA TUSBETO WA I’NDAKA UMMUL KETAABE ALAA INNA AWLEYAAA-AL LAAHE LAA KHAWFUN A’LAYHIM WA LAA HUM YAHZANOON. INNAA ROSOLO RABBEKA LAN-Y YASALOO ELAYKA, TAAHAA, HAAMEEM, LAA YUBSEROONA WA JA-A’LNAA FEE A-A’NAAQEHIM AGHLAALAN FAHEYA ELAL AZQAANE FAHUM MUQMAHOON. WA JA-A’LNAA MIM BAYNE AYDEEHIM SADDANW WA MIN KHALFEHIM SHADDAN FAAGHSHAYNAAHUM FAHUM LAA YUBSEROON. OOLAAAEKAL LAZEENA TABA-A’L LAAHO A’LAA QOLOOBEHIM WA SAM-E’HIM WA ABSAAREHIM, WA OOLAAAEKA HOMUL GHAAFELOON. LAA JARAMA ANNAL LAAHA YA’LAMO MAA YOSIRROONA WA MAA YOA’LENOONA FASAYAKFEEKAHOMUL LAAH, WA HOWAS SAMEE-U’L ALEEM. WA TARAAHUM YANZOROONA ELAYKA WA HUM LAA YUBSEROON. SUMMUM BUKMUN U’MYUN FAHUM LAA YARJEO’ON. TAASEEEM-MEEEM. TILKA AAYAATUL KETAABIL MOBEEN. LA-A’LLAKA BAKHE-UN NAFSAKA ILLAA YAKOONOO MOAMENEEN. IN NASHAA NONAZZIL A’LAYHIM MENAS SAMAAA-E AAYATAN FAZALLAT A-A’NAAQOHUM LAHAA KHAAZE-E’EN.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ بِكَ اَسْتَفْتِحُ وَبِكَ اَسْتَنْجِحُ وَبِـمُحَمَّدٍ صَلَّى اللهُ عَلَيْهِ وَاٰلِهٖ اَتَوَجَّهُ اَللّٰهُمَّ سَهِّلْ لِيْ حُزُوْنَتَهٗ وَكُلَّ حُزُوْنَةٍ وَذَلِّلْ لِيْ صُعُوْبَتَهٗ وَكُلَّ صُعُوْبَةٍ وَاكْفِنِيْ مَئُوْنَتَهٗ وَكُلَّ مَئُوْنَةٍ وَارْزُقْنِيْ مَعْرُوْفَهٗ وَوُدَّهٗ وَاصْرِفْ عَنِّيْ ضُرَّهٗ وَمَعَرَّتَهٗ اِنَّكَ تَـمْحُوْ مَا تَشَآءُ وَتُثْبِتُ وَعِنْدَكَ اُمُّ الْكِتَابِ اَلَآ اِنَّ اَوْلِيَاۗءَ اللہِ لَا خَوْفٌ عَلَيْہِمْ وَلَا ھُمْ يَحْزَنُوْنَ۔ اِنَّا رُسُلُ رَبِّكَ لَنْ يَّصِلُوْٓا اِلَيْكَ طٰهٰ حٰم لَا يُبْصِرُوْنَ وَجَعَلْنَا فِيْٓ اَعْنَاقِہِمْ اَغْلٰلًا فَہِىَ اِلَى الْاَذْقَانِ فَہُمْ مُّقْمَحُوْنَ۔ وَجَعَلْنَا مِنْۢ بَيْنِ اَيْدِيْہِمْ سَدًّا وَّمِنْ خَلْفِہِمْ سَدًّا فَاَغْشَيْنٰہُمْ فَہُمْ لَا يُبْصِرُوْنَ۔ اُولٰۗىِٕكَ الَّذِيْنَ طَبَعَ اللہُ عَلٰي قُلُوْبِہِمْ وَسَمْعِہِمْ وَاَبْصَارِہِمْ۔ وَاُولٰۗىِٕكَ ہُمُ الْغٰفِلُوْنَ۔ لَا جَرَمَ اَنَّ اللہَ يَعْلَمُ مَا يُسِرُّوْنَ وَمَا يُعْلِنُوْنَ فَسَيَكْفِيْكَہُمُ اللہُ۔ وَھُوَالسَّمِيْعُ الْعَلِيْمُ۔ وَتَرٰىہُمْ يَنْظُرُوْنَ اِلَيْكَ وَہُمْ لَا يُبْصِرُوْنَ۔ صُمٌّۢ بُكْمٌ عُمْىٌ فَھُمْ لَا يَرْجِعُوْنَ۔ طٰسۗمّۗ۔ تِلْكَ اٰيٰتُ الْكِتٰبِ الْمُبِيْنِ۔ لَعَلَّكَ بَاخِعٌ نَّفْسَكَ اَلَّا يَكُوْنُوْا مُؤْمِنِيْنَ۔ اِنْ نَّشَاْ نُنَزِّلْ عَلَيْہِمْ مِّنَ السَّمَاۗءِ اٰيَۃً فَظَلَّتْ اَعْنَاقُہُمْ لَہَا خٰضِعِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign